    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>meat-free mince </strong>to the dish with the<strong> red onion wedges </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a stir, breaking the <strong>meat-free mince</strong> up into rough, large pieces with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Crush the <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing it with the side of a knife and discard the skins</p>",
