      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>crushed garlic</strong> to the dish and stir it all up</p>",
      "order": 5,
