    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 20 min, chop the<strong> tortillas</strong> into quarters (keep them stacked for speedy chopping!)</p><p>Add the <strong>tortillas quarters</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through and lightly golden around the edges</p><p>Remove the pot from the oven and leave it covered for 5 min (this helps the flavours to develop)</p>",
