    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, tear the<strong> coriander leaves</strong> all over the<strong> oven-baked meat-free mince & black bean chilli</strong> and garnish with the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>sliced red onion</strong></p><p>Dollop over the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> all over</p><p>Serve with the <strong>baked tortilla quarters</strong> to the side for scooping</p><p>Let everyone dig in!</p>",
